        <h2 class="left-heading destination-section-heading">Berlin Wall</h2>
        <h3>Berlin Wall Memorial</h3>
        <p>North of Central Berlin is the <strong>Berlin Wall Memorial</strong>, a preserved stretch of the original Berlin Wall along a field. Nearby you can visit the Berlin Wall Memorial Visitor Center, which offers educational multimedia exhibits about the wall and its history.</p>
        <h3>East Side Gallery</h3>
        <p>Along the Spree River east of Museum Island is another preserved section of the Berlin Wall, known as the <strong>East Side Gallery</strong>. Along the walls of the East Side Gallery are over 100 large murals, many of which are political or abstract, created by artists from around the world.</p>
